article.description: — Rytis Petraitis' 18 points helped Air Force defeat South Dakota 58-57 on Sunday.
article.headline: Petraitis scores 18, Air Force takes down South Dakota 58-57
article.linkText: Petraitis scores 18, Air Force takes down South Dakota 58-57
article.story: VERMILLION, S.D. -- — Rytis Petraitis' 18 points helped Air Force defeat South Dakota 58-57 on Sunday. Petraitis added six rebounds and three steals for the Falcons (6-2). Beau Becker added 10 points while going 4 of 10 (1 for 4 from 3-point range), and they also had eight rebounds. Jeffrey Mills finished 4 of 10 from the field to finish with nine points. Paul Bruns finished with 16 points for the Coyotes (4-3). Bostyn Holt added 15 points and seven rebounds for South Dakota. Kaleb Stewart also recorded 13 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
